graph TB
    subgraph "Llama Stack Operator"
        Controller[Controller Manager<br/>Deployment]
        LlamaStackController[LlamaStackDistribution Controller<br/>Reconciler]
        MetricsService[Metrics Service<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]
        HealthProbes[Health Probes<br/>8081/TCP HTTP]
        KustomizeEngine[Kustomize Engine<br/>In-Process]
        ConfigMapWatcher[ConfigMap Watcher<br/>Controller Watch]
        NetworkPolicyMgr[NetworkPolicy Manager<br/>Reconciler]

        Controller -->|manages| LlamaStackController
        Controller -->|exposes| MetricsService
        Controller -->|provides| HealthProbes
        LlamaStackController -->|uses| KustomizeEngine
        Controller -->|watches| ConfigMapWatcher
        LlamaStackController -->|manages| NetworkPolicyMgr
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        LlamaStackDistCR[LlamaStackDistribution CR<br/>llamastack.io/v1alpha1]
    end

    subgraph "Managed Resources"
        Deployment[Llama Stack Deployment]
        Service[Llama Stack Service<br/>8321/TCP]
        HPA[HorizontalPodAutoscaler]
        PDB[PodDisruptionBudget]
        NetworkPolicy[NetworkPolicy]
        Ingress[Ingress<br/>Optional]
        PVC[PersistentVolumeClaim]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        Ollama[Ollama Server<br/>11434/TCP HTTP]
        VLLM[vLLM Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS]
        Prometheus[Prometheus]
        HuggingFace[HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    subgraph "Internal ODH/RHOAI"
        TrustedCA[odh-trusted-ca-bundle<br/>ConfigMap]
        ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>Optional]
    end

    User[User/CI] -->|creates| LlamaStackDistCR
    LlamaStackDistCR -->|watched by| LlamaStackController

    LlamaStackController -->|creates/updates| Deployment
    LlamaStackController -->|creates/updates| Service
    LlamaStackController -->|creates/updates| HPA
    LlamaStackController -->|creates/updates| PDB
    LlamaStackController -->|creates/updates| NetworkPolicy
    LlamaStackController -->|creates/updates| Ingress
    LlamaStackController -->|creates/updates| PVC

    Controller -->|CRUD operations| K8sAPI
    Prometheus -->|scrapes| MetricsService

    Deployment -->|inference requests| Ollama
    Deployment -->|inference requests| VLLM
    VLLM -->|downloads models| HuggingFace

    Deployment -.->|mounts| TrustedCA
    Deployment -.->|integrates| ServiceMesh

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style LlamaStackController fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style LlamaStackDistCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Deployment fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Service fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Ollama fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style VLLM fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style TrustedCA fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
